{"tid":351187,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"究竟咩係時間？","createTime":"2017-08-07T20:57:52.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-08T07:45:35.000Z","uid":86488,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1d707f9c003dce60ff3406e3731308e23278066e","tid":351187,"uid":86488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T20:57:52.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/vbMLqVuoQC4?t=6m40s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FvbMLqVuoQC4%3Ft%3D6m40s&d=5aqG%2BQtKOUGlo%2FnuFcCtzRFQyUQXuyYblCT5RSyYNoQ%3D&h=a7188969\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/vbMLqVuoQC4?t=6m40s</a><br />\n<br />\n我本人冇乜學識<br />\n只能夠post條片出黎<br />\n鼓勵大家參與討論<br />\n希望各位有識之士可以黎參與討論<br />\n順便讓小弟學習下"},{"pid":"7081dbaf10950858a03f4cb8ce93462c65ea7f17","tid":351187,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:02:49.000Z","msg":"time is but a stubborn illusion"},{"pid":"7193ddea94d83b201305a4ee69966344670deaf2","tid":351187,"uid":72226,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:03:13.000Z","msg":"時間係一種工具<br />\n方便量度<br />\n就好似日曆咁"},{"pid":"78abcb77a337bbb75f542fc201f76def3bb1b448","tid":351187,"uid":108937,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:12:12.000Z","msg":"時間只不過係拿來串起3d 空間<br />\n所以點解時間係第4d<br />\n<br />\n你想像下一個正立方體<br />\n其實只不過係好多個2d 正方形疊埋一齊<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n將呢個idea 放係4d<br />\n4d 的&quot;cube&quot; 只不過係好多個3d cube 串埋一齊<br />\n而串埋的方向，唔係左右，唔係上下，唔係前後，係一我地想象唔到的方向，而果一個方向，係同左右上下前後成直角的。呢到個方向，就係時間。<br />\n（好似係）"},{"pid":"6927a95171fd32eeb27b82da45674e9f92c14db9","tid":351187,"uid":44073,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:12:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"1bc4d0b8cdf166edf07cb6938c15ad2e3687429f","tid":351187,"uid":108937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-07T21:14:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Is time scalar or vector?<br />\n<br />\nWe have s = &int; v dt which is vector but E = &i